%% Data Flow Diagram: odh-model-controller
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Watch Events
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>(Istio/Envoy)
    participant Kuadrant as Kuadrant/Authorino
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTPS TLS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (RawDeployment)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, metrics Service,<br/>ServiceMonitor, ClusterRoleBinding,<br/>NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller-->>ModelReg: Sync ISVC status (opt-in)<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,Kuadrant: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Auth Setup (RHOAI 3.x)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (LLMInferenceService)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Read LLMInferenceServiceConfig<br/>Merge specs
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Gateway AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (Istio)<br/>for Authorino TLS bootstrap
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 3: Data Connection Secret Aggregation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create data connection Secret<br/>(opendatahub.io/managed=true)
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Secret)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List all data connection Secrets<br/>in namespace
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/update storage-config Secret
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over User,NGC: Flow 4: NIM Account Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>with NGC API key ref
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (NIM Account)
        Controller->>NGC: Validate NGC API key<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
        NGC-->>Controller: Validation result
        Controller->>NGC: Fetch model catalog<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
        NGC-->>Controller: Model catalog data
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NIM ConfigMap,<br/>pull Secret, Template
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 220)
        Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Flow 5: Multi-Node Ray TLS Cert Management
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Pod with multi-node label)
        Controller->>Controller: Detect Pod IP assignment
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Generate per-pod TLS cert<br/>signed by Ray CA
        Note over Controller: Ray head/worker communicate<br/>via mTLS (self-signed CA)
    end
